<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grain" width="100" height="100" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="25" cy="25" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="75" cy="75" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="50" cy="10" r="0.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grain)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .main-content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .dashboard-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3498db, #2ecc71);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .card-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: block;
        }

        .productos-card .card-icon {
            color: #e74c3c;
        }

        .pedidos-card .card-icon {
            color: #f39c12;
        }

        .sistema-card .card-icon {
            color: #9b59b6;
        }

        .card h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .btn:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db 0%, #2980b9 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ecc71 0%, #27ae60 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-success:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #95a5a6 0%, #7f8c8d 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(149, 165, 166, 0.4);
        }

        .api-section {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
        }

        .api-section h3 {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .api-buttons {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .btn-api {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #34495e 0%, #2c3e50 100%);
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .btn-api:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #34495e 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.4);
        }

        .system-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .system-info h3 {
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .info-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .info-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .info-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .info-list li i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #3498db;
            width: 20px;
        }

        .info-list li strong {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .dashboard-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .action-buttons {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .main-content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-film"></i> <%= title %></h1>
            <p><%= message %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="dashboard-grid">
                <div class="card productos-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-box-open card-icon"></i>
                    <h2>Gestión de Productos</h2>
                    <div class="action-buttons">
                        <a href="/productos" class="btn btn-primary">
                            <i class="fas fa-list"></i> Ver Productos
                        </a>
                        <a href="/productos/crear" class="btn btn-success">
                            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Crear Producto
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="api-section">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-code"></i> API Endpoints</h3>
                        <div class="api-buttons">
                            <a href="/api/productos" target="_blank" class="btn btn-api">
                                GET /api/productos
                            </a>
                            <a href="/api/productos/1" target="_blank" class="btn btn-api">
                                GET /api/productos/:id
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card pedidos-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart card-icon"></i>
                    <h2>Gestión de Pedidos</h2>
                    <div class="action-buttons">
                        <a href="/pedidos" class="btn btn-primary">
                            <i class="fas fa-list"></i> Ver Pedidos
                        </a>
                        <a href="/pedidos/crear" class="btn btn-success">
                            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Crear Pedido
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="api-section">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-code"></i> API Endpoints</h3>
                        <div class="api-buttons">
                            <a href="/api/pedidos/ultimos" target="_blank" class="btn btn-api">
                                GET /api/pedidos/ultimos
                            </a>
                            <a href="/api/pedidos" target="_blank" class="btn btn-api">
                                GET /api/pedidos
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card sistema-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-cogs card-icon"></i>
                    <h2>Información del Sistema</h2>
                    <div class="system-info">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Arquitectura Técnica</h3>
                        <ul class="info-list">
                            <li><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i><strong>Arquitectura:</strong> MVC con Separación de Intereses (SoC)</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-code"></i><strong>Controladores:</strong> Clases ES6 con async/await</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-database"></i><strong>Base de Datos:</strong> Simulada con Promesas</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-eye"></i><strong>Vistas:</strong> EJS templates modernos</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-globe"></i><strong>API:</strong> RESTful con respuestas JSON</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-server"></i><strong>Servidor:</strong> Node.js + Express</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>